Kilo
====

A tiny text editor. Built from scratch with no dependencies,
thanks to a wonderful guide at the link below from Jeremy Ruten.

http://viewsourcecode.org/snaptoken/kilo/


License
-------

Kilo was originally authored by antirez under the BSD 2-clause
license. See LICENSE for details.


Feature Ideas
-------------

* Line numbers
* Soft indent (spaces instead of tabs, backspace removes a tab
  key's worth of spaces)
* Auto indent
* Soft-wrap lines
* Copy/paste
* Config file
* Modal editing
* Multiple buffers
